    <title>Machine Translation</title>
  </header>
  <body>
<p>Our work on machine translation is based on our grammatical
analysers for Saami languages, combined with bilingual dictionaries,
grammatical transfer rules and a generation component. We build
translation programs from North Saami to Norwegian, and between Saami
languages. Giellatekno cooperates with <a
href="http://wiki.apertium.org">Apertium</a> on machine
translation.</p>

